''' Chong Yee-Voon''' ({{zh|s=鍾怡雯|p=Zhōng Yíwén}}, [[Kampar, Perak|Kampar]], Perak, February 13, 1969) is a Malaysian writer in the Chinese language. She is professor of the Department of Chinese Linguistics and Literature in [[Yuan Ze University]], Taiwan.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dayaculture.com/en/prize.php?do=viewmember&id=147|title=Da Ya Culture International|website=www.dayaculture.com|accessdate=April 18, 2018}}</ref>
She studied at the [[National Taiwan Normal University]].
